column5: I just pulled this off of my nephew Jeffs face book page. And thats all that I know about this fish for now.
Nice laker for sure , you will have to get some details when you get a chance . Congrats to your nephew
Now Thats A Laker !!! Nice, cant wait for details !
Those are the kind of cows I'm looking for!
Latest info Mike and Bill was that he caught it on a mouse pattern.
Mooooooooooooo!  Wow, that thing is HUGE!!!!!
Is it me, or is there an explosion of big fish being caught recently? Tank laker for sure!
You just love living on the edge, eh Dan?
Mouse patterns, down 80ft over 100!!  The new hotness for giant lakers!  LOL!
Now Dan, that's what's commonly referred to as "Sickloids". One heck of a fish! I'm having trouble with the picnic table on the back of the boat.
LOL Roy  Drink beers,play some cards,wait for the release.HAHA  Thats one hell of a laker Dan. Congrats to him.
